Sizer
.author
Fabbian G Dufoe
III 
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
Reports the size of selected disk objects (including subdirectories).  It
reports the number of bytes in all plain files and the number of blocks
occupied by files and directories.  It is intended for the Workbench user
who wants to know if there is room to drag-copy one or more icons.  And
binary.  
